Ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, guhera tariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Igikorwa cyo gukwirakwiza icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, kigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu byose, nubwo mu bihugu bitandukanye kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'indwara mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'amavuriro y'indembe bigomba kongera imyiteguro yo guhangana n'igitero kinini cy'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera serivisi z'ubuzima z'ubuvuzi, cyane cyane abitabwaho cyane.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2020, hamaze kugaragara icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana icyayiteye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, ubu buzwi nka SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa se SARS-CoV-2 acute acute respiratory syndrome.
Kuva icyo gihe, uburwayi buterwa no kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bwiswe icyorezo cya Koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, amakuru agera kuri 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwara indwara yoroheje yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, yaba ifitanye isano na pneumonia cyangwa nta yo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Hafi 14% by'abafite uburwayi bwa COVID-19 bwabaye uburwayi bukomeye cyane ku buryo abarwayi bagomba kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% by'abafite uburwayi bukomeye cyane bagiye mu bitaro byitabwaho cyane.
Imibare y'abapfa kubera COVID-19 mu bitaro ni hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, tugereranya n'uko byari bimeze mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turimo kandi kugereranya imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abandura COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza
Nyuma y'aho, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bice byinshi by'isi, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi na cyo kirimo kugenda gitera imbere.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere b'i Burayi bagaragayeho Coronavirus nk'uko bitangazwa n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima.
Mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu w'u Burayi, abarwayi ba mbere bemejwe n'Ubufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarukaga baturutse i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, mu bihugu 30 by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umurenge w'Ubukungu w'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza (Ubwongereza) hagezweho abantu banduye COVID-19, aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 na 31 Ukuboza 2019 hamaze kugaragara abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hamaze kugaragara abantu 1,750 banduye ndetse n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Kubona umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 n'uko bakwirakwira
Mu Kigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Gukumira no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bemejwe mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, buri munsi iboneka mu bikoresho byemewe n'amategeko, urugero nk'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima, abategetsi b'igihugu n'ab'akarere mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri ibyo bihugu, na OMS, kandi isohoka saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza no kuyigereranya n'u Butaliyani.
Nk'ishingiro ryo kumenya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, twafashe iminsi 14 y'igihe gito cyo kwiyongera ku barwayi ba COVID-19, bityo igihe gisanzwe cya COVID-19, mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abarwayi bose bagaragaye mu bihugu byombi ku isaha ya saa munani z'igitondo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 wagereranyijwe n'umubare w'abarwayi bose bagaragaye mu gihugu ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Imikorere yafashwe mu minsi 14 y'ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, mu buryo rusange, yari ihuriye n'imikorere yavuzwe mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri rusange, mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kugaragara ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma buza kwiyongera byihuse ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikubiyeho).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'imibare y'abanduye muri Italiya, ariko ibihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza na byo byagaragaje ukwiyongera kumpande zose mu kwiyongera kwa COVID-19 (ibisabwa byashyizwe hamwe).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ugereranyije n'ubwandu bwo mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Yasobanuye ko kugeza saa munani z'igitondo cyo ku wa 15 Werurwe, ibindi bihugu 15 bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye, ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza wiyongera cyane.
Imiterere y'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo cyugarije ibihugu byose ku muvuduko umwe.
Nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye byugarijwe n'ibihe bitandukanye by'icyorezo, hari itandukaniro mu buryo abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage b'ibihugu babyitabira, kandi ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibipimo bitandukanye by'abantu bagomba gukora ibizamini byemeza cyangwa ibindi byo gupima COVID-19.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'ubutayu mu Butaliyani batangaje ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ubushobozi busesuye bw'ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe muri utwo turere bwamaze kuzuzwa.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bakirwa mu bitaro cyangwa mu buvuzi bw'indembe (amakuru ntabwo agaragajwe) araboneka mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA gusa mu 6% na 1% by'ibihugu by'ibihugu by'ibihugu by'iburayi.
Ariko, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buteganyijwe kugira ngo byuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi, kandi byibanda ku mubare w'ibyabaye n'urupfu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu bijyanye no kubona ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwihariye n'ubwitonzi mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4.2 muri Porutugali ku bantu 100.000.
Ibi bivuze ko ibi bihugu bifite umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 by'ibitaro by'ubuvuzi bwihariye ku bantu 100.000 mu 2010).
Ibipimo by'uburyo bwo kuvura bifitanye isano no gukwirakwiza ubushobozi bwo kuvura hamwe n'ingengabihe kuri buri gihugu cy'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi / AEB n'ubwongereza ku bijyanye n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barembye bafite ibyago byo > 90% byo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibitaro byitabwaho cyane byatanzwe mu isuzuma rya gatandatu ry'ibyago byihuse bya ECDC bijyanye na COVID-19.
Kubera ko imibare y'abafite ubumuga bw'uruti rw'umugongo imaze kugaragara mu matsinda mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibitaro byita ku barwayi byita ku barwayi byita ku barwayi byita ku barwayi byita ku barwayi, amakuru ajyanye n'imibare y'abafite ubumuga bw'uruti rw'umugongo n'ibitaro byita ku barwayi byita ku barwayi by'uruti rw'umugongo agomba gutangwa mbere na mbere hakurikijwe uburyo bw'ibanze bw'ibanze bw'ibarura ry'uruti rw'umugongo ku kigero cya 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA ndetse no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'amavuriro by'indembe bigomba rero kwitegura guhangana n'icyiciro cy'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 buzakomeza, kandi bigakora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakire, cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barwayi, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibihe byihuse rya ECDC, gutinda gukwirakwira kwa SARS-CoV-2 bisaba uburyo bwihuse, bw'iterambere kandi bufite aho bugarukira, hamwe no guhindura imikorere y'ibanze mu kugabanya ubwandu, kuko niba nta ngamba z'ibanze zafashwe, kwiyongera kw'ibanze kw'ubwandu bishobora gutuma inzego z'ubuyobozi n'ibitaro bitagira umwanya uhagije wo kumenya, kwakira no gushyira mu bikorwa ibisubizo bikwiye.
Igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse kandi rigaragaza ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka mbi z'icyorezo.
Ibihugu bifite umwanya muto wo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya umuvuduko w'ikwirakwira ryayo, bityo bikagabanya igitutu ku buvuzi.
Iyo bidashobotse, sisitemu z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi k'Ubukungu zishobora guhura n'umuyaga munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho byihuse mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 (Syndrom Acute Respiratory Syndrome, SARS), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3.000, kandi cyateje indwara abantu barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bityo kikaba ari icyorezo cyibasiye abantu.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ari virusi ihura n'iyo SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bafatwa na SARS mu 2003, yandura mu nyamaswa z'ibinyugunyugu, kandi ishobora kuba ifite uburyo bumwe bwo gutera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Nyamara, COVID-19 ntabwo ari indwara ikomeye kandi ishobora kwica cyane nka SARS, ariko ni indwara yandura cyane kandi yibasira cyane abantu bakuze n'abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongereye w'ibitabo byanditse kuri iyi ndwara iherutse kuvuka, iki kiganiro kigamije gutanga isesengura rihuje n'igihe kandi rirambuye kuri iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi cyitabwaho cyane.
Tuzatanga amakuru y'ibanze ajyanye na Epidemiology, Etiology, Virology, Diagnostics, Therapy, Diagnostics na Prevention by'indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikomeje kubazwa, iki cyizere cyo gusuzuma iki cyorezo cy'indwara y'uburwayi ni cyo kizafasha abantu kumenya uko bakirwanya.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi udasanzwe kandi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'ikiruhuko ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo gishya cya virusi.
Iyi virusi ifite isano ya hafi na coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003, bityo ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayihaye izina rya SARS-CoV-2 n'iry'indwara ifitanye isano na yo, CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19), cyangwa COVID-19.
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyihuse kigakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri bitanu ku isi.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze kwandura abantu barenga 80.000, umubare w'abamaze kurekurwa ukaba warenze 40.000, naho abamaze gupfa bakaba barenga 3.000.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryagabishije ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage", kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko tubikesha urubuga rw'amakuru PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zisaga 200 z'ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, zirimo ibijyanye na virusi, indwara z'ibyorezo, imiterere y'umubiri, gusuzuma no kuvura, kuva inyandiko ya mbere yatangajwe ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yerekeranye n'uburyo virusi yafashwe mu bipimo by'abarwayi benshi yagenzuwe.
Iki cyifuzo cyo gusubiramo kigamije gusesengura mu buryo bwimbitse iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu nzego nshya z'ingenzi.
Mu bice by'ingenzi, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara ya coronavirus yitwa Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS yavutse mu 2012).
Tuzaganira ku byo tumaze kumenya ku bijyanye no kwirinda no kumenya indwara, ndetse no ku bibazo bikomeje kuba ingenzi.
Koronavirusi zari zisanzwe zitewe n'indwara zitera uburwayi ku bantu, zigatuma abantu 15% bahura n'ibicurane.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye inshuro ebyiri na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, byateje icyorezo cya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi byarakwirakwijwe mu bindi bihugu mu gihe gito, bituma habaho indwara nyinshi n'urupfu.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1, udusimba tw'umusonga dufite inkomoko itaramenyekana twamenyeshejwe bwa mbere Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, habonetse izindi virusi.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, nibwo hatanzwe raporo y'icyorezo cya mbere cya Fuji cyavuye i Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu ntara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, habonetse amakuru y'uko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima banduye, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko umuntu ashobora kwandurira undi muntu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, Wuhan yahawe igihe cyo gukata abantu, kandi ibikorwa by'urugendo byahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 40 bemejwe, 21 gusa ari bo bari bafite aho bahuriye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho bavuga ko indwara yatangiriye mu nyamaswa zitamenyekanye.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi.
