Nyamara, itandukaniro rya 1% riri hagati ya jenome ebyiri ni itandukaniro rinini; bityo rero, byitezwe ko haboneka ibisubizo byuzuye byemeza ko ibimenyetso bihamye (Igishushanyo cya 3).
Imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima no mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima ntabwo izwiho byinshi.
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho mu gihe cy'amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'imiterere ya in-vitro mu gihe cy'ikirere cyumye, ku kigero kiri munsi ya dogere 20 na 50%-40% y'ubushyuhe, kugeza ku minsi 5.
Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite imiterere nk'iya SARS-CoV-2.
SARS-CoV-2 yavuzwe ko ifite ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'ibinyabutabire bishobora guhosha virusi: UV no kumara iminota 30 ku kigero cya 56°C; ether, 75% ya ethanol, umuti wa chlorine, aside ya plastique, chlorophore n'ibindi bimene, ariko chlorhexidine ntabwo ifite ubwo bushobozi.
Muri rusange, abantu bose ntibashobora kwirinda SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bashobora kugira ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje neza igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Dushobora rero kwerekeza gusa ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku zindi koronavirusi, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo cya 4).
