Ubu buvuzi burimo ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe ndetse n'ubufasha bushobora kuboneka mu miti ya antiviral, imiti yo kurwanya ubwirinzi, imiti ya steroid, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa n'ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Ndetse, hari n'ibitekerezo byo gukoresha plasma y'abarwayi bakize mu kuvura abarwayi bashya.
Ibigo by'ubuvuzi birimo guhatana mu gukora udukoko tw'ubwirinzi n'urukingo rwo kurwanya virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 mu ntangiriro yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha, kandi bishobora no kwibasira ibindi bice byerekana ACE2 nk'imyanya y'ubuhumekero n'ibihaha.
Nyamara, guhumeka nabi ni byo byugarije abarwayi kandi ni na byo bituma bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, uburyo bwo guhumeka bufasha mu guhumeka ni ingenzi cyane mu guhumeka ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima bw'abarwayi, harimo imiti isanzwe ya ogisijeni, urujya n'uruza rwinshi rw'igicuri, guhumeka mu buryo butangiza umubiri no guhumeka mu buryo butangiza umubiri bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi.
