Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga ibyangombwa bya elegitoronike, gukumira no kuvura indwara z'ibanze n'imihangayiko, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi, nabyo ni ingenzi ku barwayi banduye SARS-CoV-2.
