Cytocin storm ni uburyo bwo kwanduza umubiri, buzwiho kurekura cytocin nyinshi zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izi cytoquin zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi zigabanya cyane ibinyabuzima by'ubwigenge, ari na byo bituma ARDS n'izindi ngingo zidakora neza.
Gucika intege k'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ni ngombwa mu kuvura cytoquin cyclone, cyane cyane mu barwayi bakomeye.
Corticosteroids na tosilezumab, igisubizo cya monoclonal anti-IL6, byakoreshejwe mu kuvura cytocaine cy'umuyaga.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura buhagarika ubudahangarwa bw'umuyaga wa sitokayine harimo: uburyo bwo kuvura ubudahangarwa buyobowe na T-cyle; kubuza IFN-γ, IL-1 na TNF; kubuza JAK; blinatumib; kubuza cytoquin-4 gutanga ibimenyetso; na HDAC.
