Ariko, imiti ya Steroids mu doze nyinshi ntiyagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye mu barwayi ba COVID-19 na SARS.
Ahubwo, bishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane amagufa y'amagufa aterwa na anemia, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku cyorezo.
