Mu gihe cyo kwandika iyi nkuru, nta muti wa antiviral wemewe.
Nyamara, umuti wa Remdesivir, ufatwa mu mitsi, wari ufite analogue ya nucleotide, wagize ingaruka ku murwayi wo muri Amerika wafashwe na COVID-19.
