Ku bw'ibyo, kwita ku buzima bwo mu mutwe bigomba kuboneka ku barwayi ba COVID-19, abantu bakekwaho uburwayi n'abahuye na bo, ndetse n'abaturage bose bakeneye izo serivisi.
