Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% bashobora kuba baranduye indwara zaturutse mu bitaro, harimo 17 barwaye izindi ndwara n'abantu 40 bari mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Ku bw'ibyo, kugira ngo abantu barinde ubuzima bwabo, cyane cyane abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima, abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, abagize umuryango, abakozi bakorana ndetse n'abantu basura abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye, bagomba kwitonda cyane.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bishobora kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ugutwara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa twa kirimbuzi n'udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (udupfukamunwa twa 1860s) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa two kubaga dukumira gutwara umwuka w'amazi mu mubiri uturutse ku mikaya ishobora kuba ifite uburwayi cyangwa se gutwara umwuka ku bintu, hanyuma ukayohereza ku bandi.
Ariko, udupfukamunwa twa serivisi ya N95 (numero ya serivisi ya 1860s) gusa dushobora kurinda umuntu guhumeka virusi zifite uburebure bwa 10 kugeza kuri 80 nanometero, aho 5% gusa ya virusi ishobora kwinjira; virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite uburebure buhuje na SARS-CoV, ifite hafi 85 nanometero.
Kubera ko udusimba dushobora guhura n'utundi dutanu tw'amasaka ya kirimbuzi, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bahuye n'abarwayi bagomba gukoresha udupfukamunwa N95 (Dosiye ya 1860s) kandi bakirinda kwambara udupfukamunwa twa kirimbuzi.
Usibye udupfukamunwa, abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubwirinzi buhagije kugira ngo bakureho ibyago byo kwandura virusi.
Virusi zishobora kandi kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu jisho.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95, ashobora kuba yarayanduye binyuze mu maso ye yafashwe n'indwara.
Ku bw'ibyo, abaganga bagomba gukoresha udupfukamunwa cyangwa udushumi tw'amaso mu gihe bita ku barwayi.
Mu rwego rwo kubahiriza ubuzima rusange mu turere dufite ubwandu cyangwa dushobora kubamo ubwandu, abantu basabwa gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane bakoresheje isabune, kwicungira ukwabo, kuguma mu rugo no kugabanya guhura n'abantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Abantu bagomba kuba bari kure y'abarwayi ku buryo buhagije, nko ku metero eshatu.
Ibi bikorwa bifatwa nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi igaragara nk'iyigaragara ku isi, kuba ifite isano rya hafi na SARS-CoV, byavuzwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, byatangaje ko ari umuburo ukomeye ku Bushinwa, byongeye kwibutsa icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003.
Ariko, nta gikorwa cyo guhumuriza abaturage cyakozwe mbere ya 19 Mutarama 2020, ubwo umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya indwara yatangazaga ko virusi nshya ifite ubushobozi buke bwo kwanduza no gukwirakwiza neza umuntu ku muntu, kandi ko ishobora gukumirwa cyangwa gukingirwa.
Ubwo butumwa bwatumye abantu badashishikazwa cyane n'ubwo butumwa, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari cyitegura kwizihiza Umunsi Mukuru w'Umwaka Mushya, bityo amahirwe y'ingenzi yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ku kigero gito muri Wuhan akaba yarapfuye.
Inzego zishinzwe kugenzura indwara mu Bushinwa zishobora kuba zaratojwe isomo rikomeye, maze zigakora amajyambere y'ingenzi mu bikorwa by'igihe kizaza.
Urugero, izi nzego zigomba (1) kurushaho kwitonda mu gihe zitanga amakuru ku baturage kuko ibyo zitangaza byose bizashishikaza abaturage kandi bihindure imyumvire n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kurushaho kwita ku makuru atemewe atangwa n'amavuriro aho gutegereza raporo z'ubuyobozi cyangwa abategetsi; (3) gukora cyane mu guhashya icyorezo mu bihe bya mbere aho guhamagarira abaturage gutuza; (4) gushyira amakuru ku mugaragaro mu buryo buhoraho, bufite intego kandi bw'ingirakamaro kugira ngo abantu barusheho kumenya iby'icyorezo, kandi bagakomeza gusuzuma no kunoza uburyo bwo gusubiza abaturage.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19, cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2, cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose, ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi kugeza ubu.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV, kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 na SARS bikaba bisa, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu batekereza ko SARS yongeye kugaruka.
Nyamara, hari itandukaniro ry'ingenzi hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari ingenzi cyane mu kurwanya icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bakuze n'abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore, kandi ifite ubukana n'ibipimo by'urupfu biri hejuru mu bantu bato kurusha urubyiruko.
Imibare y'abapfa bazira SARS iruta iy'abapfa bazira COVID-19 (10.91 ku 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bashobora kwanduza indwara nubwo baba badafite ibimenyetso, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bakunze kwanduzwa mu gihe indwara iba ikomeye cyane, bityo bigatuma kwirinda ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 bigorana cyane ugereranyije na SARS.
Ibi bisobanura mu rugero runaka impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira vuba cyane kandi ku kigero kinini kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19, ibipimo bisanzwe bya RNA byo gusuzuma SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba byerekana ko nta virusi ifite.
Ku rundi ruhande, abakize bashobora kongera kwandura virusi.
Ibi byatangaje ko bishobora kongera cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Nubwo ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 buteye imbere cyane, hari ibibazo byinshi bikomeye bikiriho, birimo:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo 96% by'ibinyabuzima by'umuntu umwe byabonetse hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV 2 z'imbeba, ntabwo dushobora kuvuga ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse mu myamba.
Ni iyihe nyamaswa y'ikigereranyo yafashe virusi ikava mu nyamaswa z'ibanze, ari zo mbogo, ikayigeza ku bantu?
Tutazi ibisubizo by'ibibazo 1 na 2, ntidushobora guhagarika neza umurongo w'ubwandu kandi icyorezo gishobora kongera kugaruka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo ingamba zo gukora ibipimo bya molekyuli n'ibisubizo bya shimi byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero, bityo igatuma habaho impinduka z'uburwayi zikurikiraho?
Ese virusi ishobora kwifatanya n'ingirabuzimafatizo zinyura mu bice by'umubiri?
Kugeza ubwo ibibazo bikemutse, ntituzashobora kubona uburyo bwihuse bwo kubimenya no kubirwanya.
Iki cyorezo kizamara igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ihinduka mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima mu gihe ikwirakwira hagati y'abantu?
Ese bizagaragara ko ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose, kimwe na SARS, cyangwa bizagaragara ko ari influenza?
Gusubiza iki kibazo n'ibindi byinshi ni ingenzi ariko bishobora gufata igihe.
Ariko, tutitaye ku mafaranga akenewe, uburyo bumwe rukumbi dufite bwo gukomeza ni uguhagarika icyorezo vuba na bwangu no gusubiza ubuzima mu buryo busanzwe.
Inkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs
Mu myaka ibihumbi, ihinduka ry'imiterere n'ubwumvikane byafashije mu guhinduka kw'ubwoko bumwe bwa koronavirusi (CoVs) n'ubw'abarwayi bayo, harimo n'abantu.
Mbere ya 2003, virusi ebyiri z'ubwoko bwa human coronaviruses (HCoVs) zari zizwiho kuba ziterwa n'indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'indwara y'ibicurane.
Ibimenyetso by'icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) n'icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byerekanwa ku bindi biceri, bigaragaza ubukana bw'ubwandu bwa virusi itera SIDA n'akaga kabwo.
Igitero cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, cyongeye gushyira coronavirus mu mwanya wa mbere, kidutangaza kubera uburyo bwacyo bwo guhererekanya amakuru, ariko bugira ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Ubwandu bwa HCoVs bufite inkomoko mu nyamaswa (zoonosis), kandi kumenya inkomoko mu nyamaswa ya HCoVs bishobora kudufasha cyane.
Virusi nyinshi z'ubwandu bwa muntu zitangirira mu myotsi, kuko atari indwara.
Hariho n'abaturirwa mu nkambi z'impande z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwa HCoVs.
Kumenya inyamaswa z'abaturanyi bifasha mu buryo butaziguye mu gukumira indwara mu bantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire y'abaturanyi ba coronavirus mu nyamaswa bushobora gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku bijyanye n'ubwandu mu bantu.
Muri iki cyifuzo, dutanga isesengura ry'amakuru ku mikorobe 7 ya HCoVs, twibanda ku mateka yo kuvumburwa kwayo, aho yakomotse mu nyamaswa no ku itandukaniro ry'ubwoko.
Icy'ingenzi kurushaho, turagereranya no guhangana na virusi zitandukanye z'ubwoko bwa HCoVs, duhereye ku iterambere rya virusi n'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kirimo kirasuzumwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibintu byasabwaga kugira ngo virusi igire ubushobozi bwo kwimuka hagati y'abayirimo n'ibimenyetso byayo by'uko yahindutse, na byo byatangiye gushishikaza.
Koronavirusi (CoVs) ni zo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, ukaba ugizwe n'itsinda ry'imikorere ya virusi z'uruhu rumwe rukora RNA.
Izi virusi zifite genom 26 kugeza 32 kbps, ni zo nini cyane mu virusi za RNA, zahawe izina rya "CoVs (coronavirus) " cyangwa virusi ifite ikamba kubera imiterere y'ingoma nk'iyayo.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, virusi z'ubwandu zifite ibice by'ibinyabuzima by'ingingo imwe bifite imiterere isa.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, harimo imiterere ibiri y'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwa mu buryo bwa pp1a na pp1ab.
Polyproteins zikora ibindi bikoresho kugira ngo zikore poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zitwa nsp1 kugeza kuri 16.
Poroteyine zisigaye muri genome harimo ORFs zigenewe poroteyine zigize urusobe, harimo spike (S), uruhu rwa virusi (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Hari ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwa poroteyine z'ibanze z'umuryango (lineage-specific) zandikwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa coronavirus.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro ry'ibinyabuzima, virusi za corona zigabanyijemo ubwoko bune (coronavirus alpha, coronaviruses beta, coronaviruses gamma na coronaviruses delta), muri bo ubwoko bwa beta bugizwe na virusi za corona nyinshi zo mu bwoko bwa HCoVs, kandi bugabanyijemo ubwoko bune (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso by'ibinyabuzima byerekana ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bikomokaho virusi ya alpha na beta, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikomokaho virusi ya gamma na delta.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, virusi z'ubwoko bumwe zagiye zinyura mu nzitizi z'ubwoko bumwe, kandi zimwe muri zo zaje kuba indwara z'ingenzi zibasira abantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana ubwoko burindwi bwa HCoV.
Muri byo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni byo birimo alpha-CoVs.
Izindi virusi eshanu za beta zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV), MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi bitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, urugero nko kuribwa no/cyangwa gucibwamwo.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ziherutse kumenyekana ni indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi, zigatuma abarwayi benshi barwara indwara z'ubuhumekero bw'inyuma, kandi bigatuma habaho indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ubuhumekero bukomeye (ARDS) n'ibindi bimenyetso by'ubuhumekero.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwavumbuwe mu mazuru y'abarwayi banduye indwara y'ibicurane mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, amakuru menshi yabonetse binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku cyorezo cya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi byerekana ibimenyetso by'ubwiherero.
Mu by'ukuri, mbere y'icyorezo cya SARS, byari byemewe ko ubwandu buturuka kuri HCoVs muri rusange butari bubi.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byibasiye abantu benshi muri iki gihe, aho abantu barenga 8000 banduye, kandi umubare w'abapfuye ukaba hafi 10%.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cya Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) cyatumye habaho icyorezo gikomeje muri Arabiya, n'ibindi byorezo by'ingwara zidakunze kuboneka ku isi hose.
Virusi ya Corona 2019 (2019-nCoV) nshya y'umuntu (Sars-CoV-2), ni yo yatumye icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) gikomeza, kugeza ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020, kimaze guhitana abantu 3,120 ndetse cyandura abandi barenga 91,000.
Amatara y'igitero yaraye avugijwe kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Zose zirimo ubwoko burindwi bwa HCoVs zaturutse mu nyamaswa, mu nguge no mu nyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi byemeza ko virusi za HCoVs zose zakomotse ku myuka y'ibinyugunyugu, aho virusi zihuza neza ariko zikaba zidafite ubwandu kandi zikaba zifite imiterere myinshi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyazanye imbogamizi zikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho n'umuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gukurikirana inkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs bitanga uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa amateka yabyo, imbaraga zituma habaho ihinduka ry'ubwoko n'impamvu zituma habaho ihinduka ry'ubwoko.
Bishobora kandi koroshya cyangwa kuyobora ubushakashatsi ku bikomoka ku SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, mu by'ubucuruzi no mu by'imikorere, kandi bigakoreshwa mu kwirinda ko habaho ibisa n'ibyo mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iki cyigisho cy'ubusesenguzi, dutanga isesengura ry'inkomoko y'inyamaswa, ikwirakwira hagati y'amoko, n'imikorere y'indwara ziterwa na HCoVs.
By'umwihariko, turasobanura kandi tukaganira ku bintu bisanzwe bibaho, aho virusi z'ibanze za HCoVs zisanzwe zidakora indwara mu mikinnyi yazo, ariko zikora indwara nyuma yo kwanduzwa hagati y'ubwoko ku mukinnyi mushya.
Turakomeza gusuzuma imiterere ya HCoV, aho kwiyongera kw'uburyo bwo kwanduza akenshi bijyana no kugabanuka kw'imikorere y'indwara.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje, nazo zagiye zivugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Coronavirus zo mu nyamaswa zamenyekanye mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
