Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kumenyekana virusi zirimo abantu barindwi.
Igisobanuro gito cy'amateka y'ibyavumbuwe kuri HCoVs mu gihe (Igishushanyo mbonera 1) gishobora kuba cyigisha kandi kigira akamaro.
