Hari amahirwe menshi ko izi koronavirusi zo mu nyamaswa zishobora guhinduka cyangwa se zikagira ubwandu, bigatuma habaho koronavirusi nshya zishobora kwandura abantu mu gihe kizaza kandi zikaba zangiza abantu.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa mu bice bimwe by'Ubushinwa ugomba kureka kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa batagirana imishyikirano idakenewe.
Mu gihe hazaba hari ibyago biturutse kuri SARS, MERS na COVID-19, hategerejwe gahunda nziza yo kwitegura no kwitabira.
Mu by'ukuri, virusi nyinshi zabayeho ku isi mu gihe kirekire.
Zifata umwanya wo gukwirakwiza mu byiciro by'ibanze.
Nubwo udukoko dufite ibintu byinshi bidufasha gukwirakwiza virusi, dushobora kugabanya cyane ibyago byo guhura n'udukoko n'ibindi biremwa by'inyamaswa, mu gihe abantu batojwe neza kwirinda ibyo bikoko.
Kugenzura buri gihe ibinyabuzima mu buryo bw'ibanze ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu asobanukirwe neza ibidukikije bya koronavirusi n'aho zikomoka, bikaba byamufasha kwirinda ko zishobora kwandurira ku bantu zivuye ku nyamaswa no gukwirakwira mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi kuva ku nyamaswa kugera ku bantu ni ukugirango abantu bakomeze kwirinda ahantu hazwi ho gukwirakwiza virusi zandura.
Ibice byinshi by'ikibazo cy'inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari kubura.
Icya mbere, niba imbeba zanduza virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nguge, birashimishije kureba igihe imbeba na nguge zishobora gusangira ahantu hamwe.
Icya kabiri, niba imbeba zifite uruhare rw'ibanze mu kwanduza abantu, uburyo abantu bahura n'imbeba bugomba gusobanurwa.
Icya gatatu, niba hari inyamaswa ya gatatu ifite ubwandu bwagutse, uburyo ikorana n'amoko atandukanye harimo abantu, ibinyugunyugu na pangolin, bugomba gusobanurwa.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi z'ibikururanda, harimo n'iz'ibitungwa, zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hakwiye gukorwa igenzura no gukora ubushakashatsi ku ndwara.
Yaba ari mu mukangara, ingona cyangwa ikindi kinyamaswa, SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi z'ababyeyi bayo, zimeze neza, byitezwe ko zizagaragara mu buzima busanzwe mu gihe kizaza.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri iyi ngingo buzatuma haboneka ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku iterambere rya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, ndetse no mu kwirinda no kugenzura COVID-19 mu bantu.
