Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19, ari na bwo bushya bwa mbere bwiyongereye mu munsi umwe
Ejo, Bangladesh yatangaje ko abantu batanu bapfuye ku munsi umwe kubera COVID-19.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bishwe na virusi mu munsi umwe.
Ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko abantu 114 banduye, naho 33 bagakira mu gihe bari mu rugo.
Muri rusange, hapfuye abantu 17.
Mu itangazo ry'amakuru ryashyizwe kuri interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Mirjad Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye ari abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Nk'uko muganga Mirjadi yabivuze, babiri bari bafite hejuru y'imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60 n'umwe wari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu baguye muri icyo gitero bari abo mu mujyi wa Dhaka.
