Ubucuruzi muri Ositaraliya bwagabanyije imipaka yo kugurisha udusanduku tw'ubwiherero ku gihe cy'ubucuruzi
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya ya Woolworth na Coles yagabanyije ku buryo butandukanye umubare w'amasahani y'impapuro yaguzwe, ku buryo buri duka ryaguraga rimwe, ku buryo ryaguraga amasahani abiri.
Ku wa mbere, ALDI yatangaje ko hari ibyangombwa byo kugura igikapu kimwe gusa.
Ibi bihano byashyizwe mu butumwa ku mbuga za Facebook z'amaduka n'aho guhera.
Hari amakuru avuga ko abaguzi bashyize mu bubiko soda kubera gutinya COVID-19 no kwigunga.
Ku wa Gatatu, Woolworths yakomeje kugabanya kugura impapuro z'ubwiherero zo gutumiza ku muryango w'inzu ku ipaketi imwe kuri buri tegeko.
Ayo mahinduka akurikirana na gahunda enye za mbere za buri gicuruzwa cy'ibihano byashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Mu kiganiro n'itangazamakuru cyo ku wa 8 Werurwe, Coles Supermarkets yatangaje ko nubwo hari ibitabo bine byahagaritswe, "amaduka menshi yabonye ibicuruzwa by'inyongera mu gihe kitarenze isaha imwe nyuma yo gutanga ibicuruzwa", avuga ko icyifuzo cyari "kitigeze kibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu butumwa yanditse kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri, yavuze ko ibicuruzwa byari "byarabonetse".
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuvugizi wa Woolworth, igurishwa ryazamutse "mu buryo bwihuse".
Ububiko bwa Costco muri Canberra na bwo bwagabanyije umubare w'ibikoresho byemewe mu byumweru bibiri bishize.
Mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibyo byaha, Coles yasabye ibicuruzwa binini ku batanga ibicuruzwa no kongera inshuro zo gutanga ibicuruzwa, Woolworth yasabye ibicuruzwa by'ubundi bushya, na Aldi yasabye ibicuruzwa by'ubundi bushya ku wa Gatatu.
Rachel Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Australia, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'inzego z'ibanze ku gihe cy'imodoka z'imodoka z'imodoka, yatumye bigorana.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, kuko abatanga ibicuruzwa bazakomeza guhangana n'ibyifuzo kandi bakabura ibintu byihariye.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI (ubucuruzi bw'amakaye) yatangaje ko kubera gusohora mbere y'igihe imigabane, amaduka amwe n'amwe adashobora gukora igurishwa ryihariye ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, impuguke mu bucuruzi bw'icungamutungo, Dr Gary Mortimer wo muri Kaminuza y'Ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibyangombwa buri mugoroba.
Yavuze ko umwenda w'ubwiherero ari ikintu cy'agaciro kenshi, kigomba gufata umwanya munini. Iyo ugurishijwe, umwanya munini usukura amashuka, bigatuma abantu bumva ko nta cyo bafite.
Rachel Zimmerman yabwiye ABC News ati "Coles na Woolworth bemera ko [niba] hari ibicuruzwa bihagije ku ntebe, niba hari ibicuruzwa bihagije, nk'utuyoboro two gukaraba no kwiyeza, bishoboka ko ushobora kugabanya ubwoba bwo kugura".
Uruganda rukora impapuro z'isuku zongera gukoreshwa, Who Gives a Crap, rwatangaje ko ku wa gatatu w'icyumweru gishize, ibitabo byabo byari byararangiye.
Nkuko News.com.au ibitangaza, Kimberly-Clark, ikigo gishinzwe gukora impapuro z'ubwiherero Clinix na Solaris Piper, ikigo gishinzwe gukora Sorbent, byemeje ko bakora amasaha 24 ku munsi, iminsi irindwi mu cyumweru, kugira ngo babone ibicuruzwa bikenewe ku isoko.
Urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bw'umutungo Domain.com rwatangaje ko mu gihe abaguzi bari mu kiruhuko kubera iminsi mikuru y'akazi kandi hari ibicuruzwa bike, bamwe mu bacuruzi b'umutungo baha umuguzi wa mbere w'ibicuruzwa by'i Melbourne umwenda w'ubwiherero ku buntu.
Umunara w'Umurinzi wo ku wa Kane wa NT News, ikinyamakuru cyasohokaga i Darwin, wari urimo amapaji umunani y'inyongera yari agenewe gukoreshwa nk'umwenda w'ubwiherero.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na ABC Australia ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, abikorera mu maduka babanje kwanga gushyiraho ingamba, bavuga ko nta gahunda bafite zo gushyiraho ingamba zo kugura.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ati: Ibindi bikoresho birimo udupfukamunwa, umuti wica udukoko, umutobe wo gukaraba, ifu n'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki birakenewe cyane.
