Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyize ahagaragara icyorezo cya COVID-19
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "pandemic" ryerekeza gusa ku buryo indwara yageze kure kandi nta bimenyetso byerekana uko uburwayi bwihariye bwaba bumeze, OMS yagaragaje ko ari ngombwa ko leta zigira icyo zikora ku:
"Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo".
Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi wa OMS, avuga ko "ibihugu byafata ingamba zo gusuzuma, gupima, kuvura, gushyira mu kato, gukurikirana no guhuza abantu".
" ""Turahangayitse cyane ku byiciro by'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu n'ubukana bw'indwara, ndetse no ku byiciro by'ibimenyetso by'uburangare""
Dr. Tom Friedman, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo cyari "kitari cyigeze kibaho".
Mu itangazo CNN yasohoye muri Gashyantare, yagize ati "Nta zindi virusi z'ubuhumekero zigeze zigaragara kuva ibimenyetso byatangira kugeza igihe icyorezo cyakwiriye isi yose".
Ghebreyesus na we yavuze ko atigeze abona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus.
Yakomeje ati ""Nta cyorezo na kimwe twigeze tubona gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe"."
