Gukaraba intoki ni byiza mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, cyasabye abantu gukaraba intoki nibura amasegonda 20 bakoresheje amazi n'isabune, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zanduye cyane; mbere yo kurya; nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
