Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze amabwiriza arebana n'igihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'imiti muri kaminuza ya Leeds, yavuze ko "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu kwifuza gukorakora mu maso yabo, kuko ari cyo kintu cy'ibanze cyandura indwara, bakoresheje intoki".
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, urugero nk'abita ku bantu banduye COVID-19, ariko ryemeza ko gukoresha udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC irasaba abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'umubiri tutari utwabagenewe, twakozwe mu myenda. Mu Bushinwa, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza, cyane cyane mu gihe bahuye n'abandi bantu bari hafi ya metero imwe (3m cyangwa munsi yayo), basabwa gukoresha udupfukamunwa twa muganga rimwe gusa.
Hong Kong irasaba abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu modoka z'abaturage cyangwa mu myanya irimo abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Tayilande barimo gushishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'umwenda mu ngo zabo no gukaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchecoslovaquie yatangaje ko abantu batemerewe kujya mu ruhame batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa batambaye udupfukamunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame kugira ngo bibarinde n'abandi.
Guverinoma ya Autriche yasabye abantu bose binjira mu iduka ry'ibiribwa kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Isiraheli yasabye abaturage bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Tayiwani, imaze kugera ku rwego rwo gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni 10 ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye ko kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abagenzi bo mu modoka za gari ya moshi na za bisi z'umujyi n'indi mijyi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Mu gihugu cya Panama, gukoresha agapfukamunwa ni ngombwa mu gihe uri hanze, kandi abantu badashobora kwambara agapfukamunwa bagomba kuzajya bakoresha mu rugo.
Udupfukamunwa twakoreshwaga cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapuru.
Kwitandukanya (cyitwa kandi gutandukanya umubiri) bikubiyemo ingamba zo kurwanya ubwandu zigamije kugabanya indwara binyuze mu kugabanya imikoranire hagati y'abantu.
Uburyo harimo gushyira abantu mu kato, guhagarika ingendo, guhagarika amashuri, aho bakorera, ibibuga by'imikino, amazu y'imikino cyangwa amazu y'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora kubahiriza intera hagati y'abantu baguma mu ngo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda ahantu hakunze kwiyongera abantu, bakoresha uburyo bwo gutembera batanduye kandi bakirinda gutandukana n'abandi.
