Gukoresha ijambo "kwitarura abandi" byateye abantu gutekereza ko bagomba kwifatanya mu kwibohora mu buryo bw'imibereho, aho kubashishikariza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo. Hari abayobozi batanze amabwiriza y'isuku y'imibonano mpuzabitsina muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina gusa n'uwo mwashakanye udafite ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Abantu bafite COVID-19 n'abakekwaho ubwandu basabwe kwiyicarira mu kato.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwicungira ukwabo. Leta nyinshi zashyizeho cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose baba mu turere twanduye bagomba kwicungira mu ngo zabo.
Amabwiriza yo kwicungira ukwabo akomeye cyane ni ay'abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Abantu bagiranye isano n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 ndetse n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa mu karere kagize icyorezo cy'icyorezo, bagirwa inama yo kwicungira ukwabo mu gihe kitarenze iminsi 14 kuva aho baherutse guhurira.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo cy'indwara harimo kugenzura cyangwa kugabanya icyorezo.
Ingamba zishyirwaho mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo zigamije gukurikirana no gukumira abantu banduye, no gushyiraho ubundi buryo bwo kugenzura indwara no gukingira kugira ngo bareke ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ku bandi bantu.
Iyo hatakiriho uburyo bwo gukumira icyorezo, imihati ijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zo kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka zacyo ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Hashobora gukoreshwa uburyo bwo kugabanya no gukumira.
Gukumira indwara bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane kugira ngo umubare w'icyorezo cy'icyorezo ugere munsi ya 1. Kimwe mu bikorwa byo gucunga icyorezo ni uguhagarika icyorezo kuva cyakomeye, nanone kizwi nka 'Epidemic Curve' (Gushyiraho icyorezo).
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kurengera serivisi z'ubuzima kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ubufatanye budafite imiti bushobora kugenzura ikwirakwira rya virusi harimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwigunga; ingamba rusange zigamije gutandukanya abantu, nko guhagarika amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa rusange; kwifatanya n'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwakira no kwitabira ubwo bufatanye; hamwe n'ingamba zo kubungabunga ibidukikije, nko gusukura imiterere. Igice kinini cy'ingamba zikomeye zo kugabanya icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'indwara mu Bushinwa zashyizweho igihe cyigaragazaga, nko gufunga imijyi yose no guhagarika ingendo.
Ibindi bihugu byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yo gupima abantu bose no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi itanga umuburo wo kwirinda guhora mu ngo no kwimura abantu banduye.
Singapuru yatanze inkunga ku bantu banduye bakwiyemeza kwicungira ukwabo, ndetse no gutanga ibihano bikomeye ku bantu batita ku byemezo byo kwicungira ukwabo.
Tayiwani yongereye ingano y'amasaka kandi ishyiraho ibihano bikomeye ku bikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ibigereranyo byakozwe ku Bwongereza na Amerika byerekanye ko kugabanya icyorezo (kugabanya icyorezo aho kucyumira) no kucyikuraho (guhindura icyorezo) biri mu bibazo bikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo guhindura ibintu bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu benshi bifuza serivisi z'ubuzima ku bice bibiri bya gatatu, n'urupfu ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bikomeza gutuma hapfa abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana, kandi bigatuma imibereho y'abantu benshi irushaho gukendera.
Gucika intege birashoboka, ariko bigomba gukomeza kugeza igihe virusi izakwirakwizwa mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze gukorwa, icyakurikiraho cyose), bitabaye ibyo, virusi izongera gukwirakwira mu gihe ingamba z'ubutabazi zizoroha.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhangana n'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku bukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage.
Nta muti wihariye wa COVID-19 wemejwe, ariko hari ibikorwa birimo gukorwa harimo no kugerageza imiti iboneka.
Gufata imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'ibinyamushongo, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iyo ndwara, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko umuntu afata imiti ya ogisijeni, imyuka ituma umuntu aba mu maraso, ndetse n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha steroid bishobora gutuma indwara irushaho gukomera.
Imiti itandukanye yari ifite akamaro mu kuvura izindi ndwara za virusi, irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS yavuze ko hari "uburyo bwo kuvura mu rugo n'uburyo gakondo" bushobora kugabanya ibibazo bya SARS-CoV-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryagaragaje ko kongera ubushobozi no gushyira mu bikorwa ubuvuzi mu guhangana n'uburwayi bwa COVID-19 ari ingamba z'ingenzi mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) n'ibiro by'akarere by'u Burayi by'ishami rya WHO, byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'imirimo y'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze yo guhindura uburyo mu byiciro bitandukanye birimo guhindurira serivisi za laboratwari ku gupima COVID-19, guhagarika uburyo bwo guhitamo igihe bishoboka, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ubwandu, no kongera ubushobozi bw'abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka no gutwara umwuka.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku birebana n'uwagaragaye bwa mbere (wahawe izina ry'umurwayi wa 0.)
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanyeho coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yarapfuye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Abenshi muri bo bari mu isoko ryagurishirizagamo ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Hunan, aho bagurishirizaga amatungo ari muzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora kuba yaraturutse ku nyamaswa, cyangwa se ko ishobora kuba ari zoonotic. Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, basanze indwara y'ibihaha (pneumonia) ifite icyorezo kitaramenyekana, maze bayivura kwa muganga Zhang Jian mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei, maze ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, babimenyesha ikigo cya Wuhan cya Jiangnan Disease Control Center.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku cyorezo cya "coronavirus isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani barimo Lee Wenliang, barabajijwe na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, naho undi muganga witwa Ifen, yahanwe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yazamuraga igipimo cy'ububisha.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Akarere ka Wuhan nyuma yaho yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Ukuboza, kandi imenyesha Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS).
Umubare munini w'abanduye pneumonia itaramenyekana waburiwe abategetsi b'ubuzima i Wuhan mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, bituma hatangira iperereza. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro na hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa bitewe n'imihango yo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa, kandi Wuhan ikaba ari imwe mu mijyi y'ingendo n'aho imihanda minini ya gari ya moshi ihurira.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko hari abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 banduye, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Nyuma, amakuru yemewe yagaragaje ko kugeza ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu 6.174 bari bafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi. Kugeza ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ni zo zari zifite umubare munini w'abantu bemejwe ko banduye, zirenga u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose, abantu barenga miriyoni 1.61 bari bamaze kwandura, abasaga 97.000 barapfuye, abasaga 364.000 barakira.
Mu bihugu bigera kuri 200 no mu turere, nibura hari umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho amategeko agenga imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu byose birimo ingamba zo gukumira abantu, urugero nko kuba mu ngo zabo (mu mazina nka Guma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo guhungira mu ngo cyangwa kugabanya ubwigenge) no kwirinda ingendo. Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 muri Amerika, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu rugo, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine, hafi miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo na miliyoni 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu rugo.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu buryo runaka bwo kwigunga, ariko hashize iminsi ibiri, uwo mubare wariyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2,6, ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko afite COVID-19 yavutse ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo itemejwe ivuga ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr. Zhang Jixian, yagaragaje igitsure cy'abarwayi bafite Pneumonia ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, ku mpamvu itaramenyekana, maze ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, ibitaro bye byahise byibwira Ikigo Gishinzwe Kugenzura Indwara cya Jianghan Wuhan.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'abarwayi byakozwe ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko hari virusi itera SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Akarere ka Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Mu gihe itangazo ryasohokaga, polisi yaburiye abaganga bo muri Wuhan ko hari "ibihuha" by'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya gifatika" cy'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye, nyuma yaho umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping, yabyise "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
"Mu gihe cy'ibyavuzwe ko ari" uguhagarika abantu mu buryo bukabije mu mateka y'abantu, "ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe umwenda w'ubuzima wahagaritse ingendo n'ingendo z'abantu bajya/va i Wuhan, kandi wageze mu mijyi 15 yo mu mujyi wa Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57".
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byarabujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu bice byinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje kandi ko hubatswe ibitaro by'agateganyo, Huoshenshan Hospital, byamaze iminsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hakurikiyeho ibitaro byitwaga Leishenshan Hospital kugira ngo haboneke abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho ingamba nyinshi zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bantu batemberezaga no kongera igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kafashe ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ibikorwa by'urugendo zashyizwe mu bikorwa mu bice bitandukanye by'Ubushinwa.
Imihango yo kugabanya ingendo mu ntara ya Hubei no hanze yayo.
Itumanaho rusange ryabaye nk'ibikoresho by'urugendo, kandi amazu ndangamurage yafunzwe by'agateganyo mu Bushinwa hose.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abaturage bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bashyizwe mu byemezo byo guhagarika ingendo. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyadutse ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 y'igenzura ry'inzira ku banyamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bwari bufite umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gihugu, mu minsi itanu mbere yaho, wanduye mu rugendo rwahereye i Wyatchabul rwerekeza i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Li Keqiang, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyahagaritswe mu gihugu ndetse ko icyorezo cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingamba zo mu ngendo mu bice byose bya Hubei usibye Wuhan zaragabanyijwe nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko kwinjira mu gihugu ku baturage n'abafite viza bizasubikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ndetse nta makuru arambuye yerekeye igihe iyo gahunda izamara.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula ya Chine.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije abacuruzi gutangira imirimo yabo ku ya 30 Werurwe, ndetse itanga n'amafaranga yo gushyigikira ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo gupfusha abaturage mu gihe cy'iminota itatu yo guceceka ku rwego rw'igihugu saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba ku ya 4 Mata, mu gihe habaye ibirori bya King Ming Festival, nubwo leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango ku buryo bwa interineti kwirinda gutandukana mu buryo bw'umubiri mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yanduye Koreya y'Epfo ivuye mu Bushinwa ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima n'ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habaye ukwiyongera kw'abanduye, ahanini biturutse ku bantu bari bateraniye i Daegu mu muteguro mushya witwa Shincheonji Church of Christ.
Abashyigikiye Shincheonji bari bahuye na Daegu i Wuhan bakeka ko ari yo virusi ikomokaho.
Kuva ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336, 1261 cyangwa 13% by'abayoboke b'itorero bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite imibare yo ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hemejwe ko hari abantu barenga 2000 banduye, ku ya 29 Gashyantare habonetse abantu 3150.
Ibigo bya gisirikare byose bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bagaragaye ko banduye coronavirus.
Ibibazo by'ibihe by'indege na byo byarabangamiwe, bituma na byo bihinduka. Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ni yo gahunda nini kandi iteguye kurusha izindi ku isi yo gupima abaturage bakekwaho virusi no gutandukanya abantu banduye, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na yo.
Uburyo bwo gupima burimo kwemeza by'agateganyo ibimenyetso ku bantu bashya binjira mu ngendo mpuzamahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu za terefone ngendanwa, gupima kuri farashi virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20.000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo, nubwo nta mijyi yose ifunze, ni intambwe nziza mu kugenzura icyorezo. Mu mizo ya mbere, sosiyete ya Koreya y'Epfo yagize ibibazo byinshi mu gisubizo Perezida Moon Jae-in yatanze kuri iki kibazo.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yo kwamagana ibyo bavuga ko ari ubugome bwa leta mu gucunga icyorezo, mu gihe abandi bashimye uko yabyitwayemo.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, ari bwo bwa mbere mu byumweru bine bwagize umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi umwe.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bazatangira kwinjira mu gihugu bavuye hanze, bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yahawe inkunga n'ibihugu 121 byo gukora ibizamini bya virusi.
Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 byemejwe kuwa 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho abantu babiri bapfuye kuri uwo munsi nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, amarushanwa ya siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no guhagarika kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari 5 za Riyal mu kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 yavuze ko nta gahunda ihari yo gushyira mu kato uturere dufite virusi, ko abantu ari bo bonyine bagomba kujya mu kato.
Imyiteguro yo kugabanya ingendo zo hanze y'umujyi yatangaje muri Werurwe, ariko urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi y'igihugu rwarakomeje mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Irani.
Ahantu hatagatifu ha Shia mu mujyi wa Qom hafunguye ku ba mukerarugendo kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo guhishira amakuru ku cyorezo cya virusi muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byatangaje ko Iran ari yo ifite abantu banduye kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko icyorezo cya virusi gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, kandi 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 bavuze ko basuzumye ko banduye virusi ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Umugenzuzi w'uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura by'agateganyo abarwanashyaka bazira ko bazira ibitekerezo byabo mu mahoro, kandi bagasaba ko imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira bwo gufungwa zifungurwa by'agateganyo.
Hari amakuru avuga ko ahantu hafunze, urugero nk'ibigo by'imfungwa, aho nta buvuzi bwiza, hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ari na bwo bushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko ari bwo bwa mbere muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 n'abayobozi bakoreraga leta cyangwa abahoze bayikorera muri Irani barapfuye.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rumwe rufatika rwa coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, mu gihugu cya Irani, abantu banduye bashobora kuba baruta inshuro eshanu abo byatangajwe.
Byongeye kandi, byatangajwe ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko hagabanywa igitutu cy'ubukungu ku bihugu byibasiwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, harimo na Irani.
