Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaje ko badafite ubwandu ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibipimo by'abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 ku kibuga cy'imyidagaduro cya Ranch, kubera kwirinda, byatangaje ko batagira ubwandu.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yakuye ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo cya pandemic.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Pakisitani, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byoherereje u Bushinwa imfashanyo.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bice bya China byazahajwe na coronavirus. Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, itsinda ry'abakozi ba Chicago Metropolitan Area ryashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'uburyo bwo kuvura no gushyigikira "abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, leta y'Ubushinwa yahaye Filipinos udupfukamunwa ibihumbi 200, nyuma yaho Senateri Richard Gordon yoherereje Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa miliyoni imwe i Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze miliyoni 18 z'intoki z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi harimo imyenda ihenze 10.000, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zohereje inkunga y'amafaranga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu bihugu byanduye. Nyuma y'uko ubwandu mu Bushinwa bwagaragaraga ko bufite ubushobozi, icyo gihugu cyafashije ibindi bihugu byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu gufasha Ubutaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umucuruzi w'icyamamare Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'amapaketi 60000 y'imyenda yo kurinda umubiri, mu gihugu cya Ethiopia, Addis Ababa, kugira ngo bitangirwe n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Yakomeje kohereza muri Panama ibikoresho byagenewe gupima 5000, udupfukamunwa 100.000 na za ventilateur 5.
"Twagiye dutanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'Ubushinwa".
Urugero, Espagne yanze gukoresha ibikoresho by'igerageza byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite 30% by'ubunyangamugayo, mu gihe Ubuholandi buvuga ko mu Bushinwa hakoreshejwe udupfukamunwa 600,000 dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwanze kwakira udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutakiri mu bubiko, buvuga ko ari utwo mu Bushinwa, ariko ko mu by'ukuri ari utwo muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, imfashanyo z'u Bushinwa mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika, zakiriwe mu buryo bufatika. Guhera ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi by'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryashimiye abayobozi b'Ubushinwa ku mihati bashyizeho mu kugenzura no gukumira iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryagereranyije ibi n'icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga guhisha amakuru, bigira ingaruka mbi ku mihati yo gukumira no kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, kandi muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo, leta y'u Bushinwa "yashyizeho gahunda yo gutanga amakuru buri gihe mbere y'ibiruhuko by'umwaka mushya w'izuba, kugira ngo ikureho icyorezo cy'indwara".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, uhagarariye Umuryango Mpuzamahanga wita ku Buzima, Goden Galle, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyo gushyiraho gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo i Wuhan, yatangaje ko ""nta gushidikanya ko atari inama y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima"" ariko ko ""ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo kwiyemeza gukumira iki cyorezo aho kiri hasi cyane kurusha ahandi hose"" avuga ko ari "ntaho byari byigeze bibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu banduye abantu hanze y'Ubushinwa kandi umubare w'abantu banduye mu bindi bihugu na wo wiyongera, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima watangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icy'ubutabazi mpuzamahanga, kikaba ari icya gatandatu kuva habaho icyorezo cya mbere cy'ibicurane by'ibicurane mu mwaka wa 2009. "
Tedros Adhanom, Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko PHEIC ifite "ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make n'agati, kandi bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwita ku buzima".
Mu gusubiza ku byemezo by'ingendo, Tedros yatangaje ko: "Nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zidakenewe zigenga ingendo n'ubucuruzi ku isi" yongeraho ko "Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ritagombye gushyiraho ingamba zo kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gutanga inkunga yo gufasha ibihugu bifite amikoro make mu kwitegura, ugaragaza ko ari ngombwa gufasha ibihugu "bifite uburyo buhagije bwo kumenya abantu banduye cyangwa bafite ibimenyetso".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dukomeye ku buryo tudafite aho duhuriye na bo" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa se ukazishyura inshuro ebyiri nyuma". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryashyize ahagaragara icyorezo cyitwa COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Antonio Guterres, yemeye ko "ingamba zo kongerera gahunda y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu guhangana n'indwara" zikoreshwa.
Ibi byatumye itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ry'ubuyobozi bw'ibibazo ryinjira mu bikorwa kugira ngo rishobore guhuza ibisubizo byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, kandi nkuko bivugwa na OMS, bizatuma "bishyiriraho intego yo kwibanda ku buryo bwo kuvura, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gushyira mu bikorwa ubuhanga bwazo mu nzego z'imibereho, ubukungu n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika ry'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa ryayobowe na OMS ryashyizweho mu rwego rwo gutanga ubuhanga mpuzamahanga n'ishami rya OMS mu rwego rwo gufasha mu bijyanye n'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu no gupima "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'icyorezo" mu Bushinwa, binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo ku butaka kugira ngo bapime "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'intara/intara harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu".Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo gishobora kuba icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo ari kare cyane ko cyitwa icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba "gushyiraho gahunda yo kwitegura".
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza iki cyorezo cya Iran, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ibipimo by'ibyago bya coronavirus ku isi byavuye kuri ""habyinshi"" bigera kuri ""habyinshi cyane"".
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ubutabazi mu bihe by'ibihe bidasanzwe muri OMS, mu itangazo yatanze yatanze umuburo agira ati ""Ni ukuri ku butegetsi bwose ku isi: kubyuka".
"Virusi iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura, ukibuka ko uko wabyitwaramo neza bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ""kugenda nabi kurushaho"".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemeza ko abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange batangaza ko icyorezo cyugarije isi yose, kuko kuvuga ko "twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azandura iyi virusi" ari byo bisobanura.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo ku isi.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo by'umubare w'ibimenyetso by'icyorezo n'ibipimo by'ibimenyetso by'uburangare". OMS yanenzwe cyane kubera ko icyorezo cyagaragaye ko kitari cyagenwe neza, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko habonetse ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi muri pandemic".
Igisubizo cya politiki cyari gikubiyemo gusaba umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom kwegura, byasinywe n'abantu 733.000 kuva ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU zigera kuri mirongo zashimangiye ko uburenganzira bw'abantu bufite agaciro mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko ingamba zo kurokora abantu zigomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa kandi ko ari inshingano za leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kuba umuntu adafite amafaranga cyangwa nta bwishingizi bw'ubuzima, bidakwiye kuba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni abantu runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abana bato, abatishoboye, abahunze, abatagira aho baba, abafite ibibazo bikomeye, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya Leta mpuzamahanga birimo gucunga ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19.
OEC yashyizeho ikigo cyo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi yuzuye ku bijyanye n'imyitwarire y'ibihugu ku isi, ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Guhera ku miyoborere yo gukomeza sisitemu y'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi yose kugeza ku gusuzuma ingaruka z'igenzura n'amategeko agenga ingendo, Digital Hub ikubiyemo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu (uburyo ibihugu bisubiza iki kibazo), igamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku byaranze buri kimwe no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose gihuje ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bwongereza Michael Gove na Eduardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Jair Bolsonaro, kubera ko yagabanyije icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'intara b'ishyaka rya gikomunisti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera ubuyobozi bwabo mu rwego rwo gushaka gushyiraho ihagarikwa ry'abimukira mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, bigaragaza kutishimira uko inzego za politiki zabyitwayemo muri ako karere.
Bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari ugukingira umunyamabanga mukuru wa Communist Party of China, Xi Jinping, kubera uburakari bw'abaturage kuri we mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bakuru b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze kumenya hakiri kare icyorezo cya Wuhan coronavirus, bituma Amerika n'Ubutaliyani byemeza ko Ubushinwa ari bwo bwa mbere bwagize uruhare mu cyorezo cya COVID-19.
"Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika buvuga ko coronavirus ari ""virusi y'Abashinwa"" cyangwa ""virusi ya Wuhan"" kandi buvuga ko ""kugenzura byatumye virusi ihitana ubu yabaye icyorezo ku isi yose"" aho bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari ivangura ry'amoko ndetse ko ""byatandukanyije ibitekerezo ku bushobozi bwa leta ye bwo kurwanya iyi ndwara".
Daily Beast yabonye umurongo wa televiziyo ukoreshwa n'inama y'igihugu ishinzwe umutekano, ikoresha uburyo bwitwa "Byose biri munsi y'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa".
Turasabwa gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo ubutumwa bwacu bugere ku bantu mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru no gutanga ibiganiro kuri televiziyo. " Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imihati y'u Bushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa byayo byo kwamamaza kugira ngo bigire ingaruka ku isi. "
Joseph Borel, umutegetsi wa EU ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga, yatanze umuburo ati ""hariho igice cya geopolitiki kirimo kugerageza kugira ingaruka binyuze mu guhinduranya ibitekerezo no 'uguha agaciro.'"
Burrell yakomeje avuga ko "Ubushinwa bushishikajwe cyane no kugaragariza bose ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufasha wizewe kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Siriya, Venezuela na Irani kugira ngo bufashe ibihugu byombi, mu gihe kugeza ubu bwohereje inkunga nyinshi ku bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Ibipfamatwi 100.000 Jack Ma yari agiye guha Cuba byahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Mata kubera ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Abategetsi ba Amerika bakomeje gushinjwa ko bohereje inkunga z'ibindi bihugu mu gihugu cyabo.
Hari n'ibindi bihugu byavuze ko hari amakimbirane ku bijyanye n'udupfukamunwa, urugero nk'u Budage, Autriche na Suisse, kimwe na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe amagana y'imodoka za ventilateur zari zigiye muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze EU kubera ko itabashije gukorana n'u Butaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwitabiriye.
"Birazwi neza ko ibyo bidashimisha ubumwe bw'u Burayi""".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani, Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya, Vladimir Putin, yohereje ingabo z'Uburusiya mu Butaliyani kohereza imiti ya gisirikare, ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byihariye n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n' "abantu batari bazwi mu rwego rwo hejuru mu bya politiki", kivuga ko 80% by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "zitari zikenewe cyangwa zitari zifite akamaro kanini".
Uwo mushyingiro yashinje u Burusiya gukoresha nabi "ibihe bya politiki na dipolomasi" mu gikorwa cy'ubuhemu.
Atilio Fontana, Perezida wa Lombardy na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, banze ibivugwa n'itangazamakuru bashimira ibyo bikorwa.
Uburusiya bwohereje indege itwara ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Dmitry Peskov, umuvugizi wa Kremlin, yagize ati "igihe twatangaga ubufasha ku bakoranaga muri Amerika, twashyize imbere ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'imiti muri Amerika bazongera gukora, na bo bazaba bashobora kudufasha mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imikino ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu by'Abanya-Baltique, ni imyitozo ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izakorwa ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, Keith Hudson yanenze imikorere ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho ubu, ntabwo ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi biri mu kaga, ahubwo ubuzima bw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bikorerwamo ibikorwa na bwo burageramiwe". Leta ya Irani yibasiwe cyane na virusi, kandi abanyamuryango bagera kuri makumyabiri na bane b'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko, hamwe n'abandi bantu 15 bakomeye muri politiki cyangwa ba mbere, banduye iyi ndwara".
Perezida wa Irani, Hassan Rouhani, yoherereje abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa ifunguye ku wa 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo guhangana n'icyorezo kubera ko kitagishoboye kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani. Iki cyorezo cyateye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gushyiraho politiki z'imibereho myiza zisanzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo kwita ku buzima ku isi hose, kwita ku bana ku isi hose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihabwa uburenganzira, n'amafaranga menshi y'ubuzima rusange.
Abahanga mu bya politiki bavuga ko icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku amahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya Perezida ya 2020 ndetse no ku mubano w'u Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo.
Nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangarije ko buzakumira abagenzi bose bavuye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta, Koreya y'Epfo yanenze u Buyapani kubera "uburyo budafite ishingiro kandi budafite icyo buvuga ku mihati yo gushyira mu kato".
Abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo batangiye kugira impungenge z'uburyo Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo muri iki kibazo.
Abantu benshi bo muri Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba Moon kwegura, bavuga ko ari ukubera ko leta itagize icyo ikora mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa se ko yashimye uko yabyitwayemo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemererwa gushyiraho amategeko y'ubutabazi kugira ngo bikurikize ibyifuzo by'igihugu.
Hari bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagize impungenge ko bishobora gutuma leta zigira imbaraga nyinshi.
Muri Hongiriya, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y'icyo gihugu yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orbán ashobora gutegeka igihe kitagira ingano, ko Inteko Ishinga Amategeko n'amatora byahagaritswe, kandi ko abatanga amakuru atari yo ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo leta ikemura ikibazo cyabayeho bagomba guhanwa.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatewe n'ibimenyetso byinshi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho, byatewe no kongera ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus, gutinya kugura no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikorwaremezo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ikomeje kwiyongera k'ibyifuzo by'abaguzi n'ikibazo cy'abatanga imiti.
Mu turere twinshi, hakomeje kubaho ibikorwa byo guhaha by'abaturage, bituma amaduka abura ibicuruzwa by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yabonetse, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibikoresho.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga rwagaragaje ko rwibaza ku gutinda kohereza ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongera inshuro 20 ku biciro bisanzwe, bituma haboneka ibyangombwa by'ubuvuzi bifata amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi kandi byateje ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi, kandi Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko ubuzima bw'abakozi buzaba bugarijwe n'akaga.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi ba Diego babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye mu maduka amwe n'amwe haboneka ibyokurya bike, bituma leta ya Australia ibyibuza. Nubwo hari abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, kandi hakaba hari n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, nta na kamwe muri utwo turere kagize ibyago bikomeye byo kubura ibiribwa.
Ingamba z'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ingengabitekerezo n'ubucuruzi butemewe bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze zagize icyo zigeraho, kandi zirinze ibura ry'ibiribwa ryari ryarahanuwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Ibikorwa by'ubuhinzi mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, aho ubutaka bukora cyane, ntibyigeze bigabanuka cyane, ariko abahagarariye uwo mugabane bavuga ko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka.
Amashami y'ibiribwa adafite aho ahurira n'i Wuhan yabaye ay'akanya gato, mu gihe abayobozi bakuru b'Ubushinwa bafunguye ibigega by'ingurube kugira ngo barebe ko abaturage bafite ibyokurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo mu Butaliyani asaba abahinzi kubika ibiribwa mu gihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe.
Ubukungu bw'isi bwarababaye mu Bushinwa: Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba za leta zo kwirinda icyorezo, aho ubucuruzi bwaguye ku kigero cya 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari kimwe mu bihugu by'ingenzi by'ubukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi kigamije guhungabanya ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo muri Economist Information Unit yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe hazaba hagiye kugaragara neza ibisubizo by'ibiza.
