Ibizamini byo muri laboratwari by'indwara ya Coronavirus yo mu guhumeka 2019 (COVID-19) na SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano, birimo uburyo bubiri, uburyo bwo kumenya ko hari virusi n'uburyo bwo kumenya ko hari udukoko tw'umubiri twatewe n'ubwandu.
Kuboneka kwa virusi mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR, ikora RNA ya coronavirus.
Ni ikizamini cyihariye kandi kigamije gusa kumenya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ya RNA.
Bikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyangwa bushya.
Gucukumbura udukoko tw'umubiri (serumology) birashobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'umubiri byerekana umubare w'abanduye, harimo n'abari bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje ku buryo bitari ngombwa ko babimenyesha cyangwa nta bimenyetso by'uburwayi bari bafite.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu n'ubwirinzi bw'amatungo bishobora kumenyekana hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'ibipimo.
Kubera ibipimo bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku cyorezo cya virusi mu baturage.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ku mubare w'ibizamini byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye byo ku isi.
Guhinduka bishobora no kugira ingaruka ku mibare y'abapfa bivugwa ko yiyongera cyane, bikaba bishobora kuba byaravuzwe mu buryo buteye ubwoba cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hifashishijwe uburyo bwa rRT-PCR (polymerases-reverse transcription chain reaction), ibipimo bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo byo mu mwuka biboneka mu buryo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo by'umwimerere cyangwa ibipimo by'umwimerere.
