Iperereza rya RT-PCR ryakozwe mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'uburwayi hakoreshejwe ingufu z'amaraso gusa, ryagaragaye ko ari ryiza.
Nyuma yacyo, virusi ishobora guhita ipfa mu muhogo, nubwo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bageragejwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, bashobora guhabwa ibipimo by'ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero, hakoreshejwe intoki cyangwa se bakagirwaho isuzuma.
Imwe mu ngero za mbere za PCR yateguwe muri Mutarama 2020 na Charité i Berlin, yakoresheje polymerases z'uruziga (rRT-PCR) z'ubundi buryo, zitanga urufatiro rwo gukora ibikoresho 250,000 byatanzwe n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
