Igice cy'igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku ndwara ni ugukora udukoko tw'umubiri twitwa IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima abantu mu gihe cy'iminsi 7 cyangwa irenga nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, mu kumenya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri no kugenzura abaturage. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa mu ma laboratwari nkuru (CLT) cyangwa mu igenzura ry'aho umuntu agenewe (PoCT).
Ibipimo by'ibanze bizaba bigishobora gukorwa mu mabari menshi, ariko kuboneka bizaterwa n'umusaruro wa buri buryo.
Ubusanzwe CLT ikorwa hakoreshejwe amaraso amwe, ariko hari n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bishobora gukoreshwa.
Mu gihe cyo gukora PoCT, amaraso avamo urugero, akenshi avamo uburyo bwo kuvoma.
