Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bita isuku y'intoki, bisobanura igikorwa umuntu akora kugira ngo akureho umukungugu, ibinure, udukoko duto duto cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe ku ntoki.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu buryo buhoraho mu "bihe bikomeye" ku munsi, bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane n'icyorezo, byandurira mu nzira y'amaraso.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa gucibwamwo, iyo badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa (urugero, mu mazuru).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi byo gukaraba intoki n'isabune ku munsi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara: nyuma yo gukaraba (kugeza amenyo n'amaraso), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana (kuhindura amagi), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa igihe ukorakora ku nyama mbi, amafi cyangwa amagi.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje ivu. Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) ushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki.
