Ubuvuzi bw'amaboko bwerekeza ku bikorwa by'ubuvuzi bifitanye isano n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukoresha imiti cyangwa imiti bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ukuzikuramo indwara ziterwa n'ibicurane (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho bya kirimbuzi bishobora gutera uburwayi cyangwa indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu by'imirire cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane bya grippe, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zandura; kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'ibicurane; no kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
