Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, impfu z'abana ziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ibicurane zishobora kugabanuka hifashishijwe ibintu byoroheje umuntu yakora, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Ibi byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa muri izi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Uburyo bwo kuvura bushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bushobora kugabanya igifu ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, ku buryo buhuye no kubona amazi meza mu turere dufite amikoro make.
48% by'ibyago byo kugabanuka kw'ibicurane bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (ARI), bikunze gukorerwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu miryango hirya no hino ku isi.
