Kwirinda ibyago byo mu kazi kubera COVID-19
Kugabanya ibyago byo mu kazi kubera COVID-19 bisobanura gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zo kwirinda no kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugabanya ibyago mu kazi neza biterwa n'aho ukorera n'inshingano ufite, kandi birashobora guhinduka bitewe n'igenzura ry'ibyago bituruka ku bantu bahura n'indwara, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage ndetse n'impamvu z'ibyago ku mukozi wese ushobora kuba afite ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ibiro bishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA) by'Amerika, akazi gafite ibyago bike gafite umubare muto w'abantu bahuye n'abandi bakozi, kandi kagirwa inama yo gufata ingamba nke zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukoresha udupfukamunwa no gukora isuku buri gihe no kwirinda indwara.
Muri ibyo bikorwa harimo n'iby'ubucuruzi bufite ibyago bito, aho usanga abantu batagomba guhura cyane cyangwa ngo bagirane imishyikirano ya bugufi n'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora guhura n'ikibazo cy'ibiza bitewe n'uko bahura n'abaturage cyangwa se ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bakorana n'abaturage mu bigo by'amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo y'akazi hakunze kubamo abantu benshi ndetse no mu maduka amwe n'amwe manini acuruza ibicuruzwa.
Kugabanya ibyago kuri aba bantu, birimo kuboneza umwuka ukoresheje filtri z'umwuka zikora neza, kwirinda guhekenya no kubona ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku muntu ufite COVID-19, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima bafite uburwayi bwa COVID-19 bakorana n'abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 ari abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi, cyane cyane iyo bakoresha uburyo bwo gutunganya Aerosol cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 cyangwa bafite uburwayi.
Mu byatuma abakozi bakenera kugenzura ibyago byo ku kazi harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, urugero nk'ibyumba bifite umwuka mubi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batakiri ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kuba bagomba kwita ku bandi, cyangwa gutinya kurwara.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bikenewe ndetse no mu buryo bwo kubikura (nk'ubuguzi mu masaha y'ikiruhuko cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga ibicuruzwa aho bikenewe cyangwa ku magare).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere twibasiwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guteza ibibazo. Gahunda yo kwitegura no gusubiza indwara zandura ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ingamba zo kwirinda.
Ibipimo byibyago bijyanye n'aho ukorera ndetse n'imirimo itandukanye, harimo aho umuntu yabonetse, ibyago by'ubuzima n'ibyago by'ubuzima ku mukozi ku giti cye, harimo no kurwara indwara idakira.
Nanone, hazashyirwaho uburyo bwo kugenzura neza kugira ngo birinde izi ngaruka, kandi hashyirweho gahunda z'uko byagenda mu gihe hashobora kuba icyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza indwara zandura bishobora gukorwa hakurikijwe inama zatanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa urw'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura indwara zihurikiyeho, kubungabunga ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo mu miyoboro itanga ibicuruzwa.
Uburemere bw'iki cyorezo mu baturage, aho ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi biherereye, bigira ingaruka ku bisubizo by'abakize.
Urutonde rw'ibyago byo kugenzura ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu kwita ku buzima n'umutekano mu kazi, kugira ngo bigenzurwe hakurikijwe uko ingaruka zabyo zingana.
Aho bishoboka ko ingufu za COVID-19 zidakurwaho, uburyo bwo kugenzura mu buryo bw'ubwubatsi, hanyuma hakurikijwe uburyo bwo kugenzura mu rwego rw'ubuyobozi, ndetse n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite, ni bwo buryo bwo kugenzura bufite imbaraga.
Igenzura ry'ubwubatsi rigamije kuvana abakozi mu bintu bishobora kubateza akaga mu kazi, ariko ntirishingiye ku myitwarire y'umukozi, kandi bishobora kuba ari byo bikora amafaranga menshi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ibiro ni ihinduka ry'amabwiriza cyangwa imikorere y'akazi abakozi cyangwa abakozi bagomba gukurikiza.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bifite ingaruka nke ugereranyije n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi n'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, ariko bishobora gukumira ibyago bimwe na bimwe.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku ngaruka zishobora guteza abakozi, gushyirwa mu buryo bukwiye (urugero: udupfukamunwa), gukoreshwa buri gihe kandi buri gihe, kugenzurwa, gusana, gusimbuzwa, gufungura, gusukura no kongera gushyirwa mu gihe bibaye ngombwa cyangwa gutwika mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwandura.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano (OSHA), abakozi bafite ibyago bike byo kwandura ni abafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abaturage cyangwa abandi bakozi.
Mu ngamba zo kwirinda indwara abantu bo mu nzego zose z'akazi bagirwa harimo gukaraba intoki buri gihe, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero, ndetse no gutwikira umunwa mu gihe bakorora cyangwa basese, kubona impapuro z'ibumba n'ibisukika, kwitegura kuvugana n'abantu bavuye kure cyangwa gukora amasaha atari kugenga mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, gushishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibindi bikoresho no kugira gahunda ihoraho yo gusukura no gukumira ubwandu.
Kumenya no gukumira vuba abantu bashobora kwandura ni ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abakiriya n'abandi bantu bari mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyasabye abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso byose bizashira, nibura amasaha 24 nyuma yo guhagarika gukoresha imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa imiti ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi hashyirwaho gahunda yo korohereza abakozi mu gihe cyo kuruhuka mu buryo bwo kuvura kugira ngo abakozi bagume mu rugo bita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi abakozi bose bamenyeshejwe aya mabwiriza mashya.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ibiro bya OSHA, akazi gafite ibyago biciriritse ni akazi gasaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi n'abandi, kandi akabatandukanya hafi cyane, mu ntera ya metero 1.8, kandi ntibiramenyekana niba umuntu afite ubwandu bwa COVID-19, ariko ashobora kuba afite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 kubera ko aba mu baturage cyangwa mu bihugu bitandukanye yagiye mu bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Muri aba harimo abakozi bafasha abaturage, nk'abakora mu mashuri, aho bakorera cyane n'ahandi bakorera ibicuruzwa byinshi, hamwe n'abakora mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ubucuruzi. Ingamba z'ubwubatsi z'iyi kipe n'iz'abandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura COVID-19 zirimo gushyiraho udupira tw'umwuka tw'ubuziranenge, kongera ibiciro by'ubushyuhe, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'izirinda imibavu ya plastiki, no gushyiraho udupfunyika tw'abakozi bakoresha imashini z'ubuziranenge. Ingamba z'ubuziranenge z'izi kipe n'iz'abandi bafite ibyago byinshi zirimo: gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gushishikariza abakozi gusimbuza amateraniro yo gufungura imyenda, gushyiraho amasaha y'akazi ahindagurika, guhagarika ingendo z'akazi zidakenewe mu bice by'akazi birimo ubwandu bwa COVID-19, gushyiraho gahunda z'akazi, gushyiraho gahunda z'ibanze zo guhangana n'akazi, gutanga amabwiriza yo guhangana n'ibimenyetso by'ibyago, kwigisha abakozi kubijyanye n'uburwayi, kurinda ku buryo bw'umubiri, no kugabanya ubukana bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze bikingira abantu cyangwa abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubwubatsi bikoresha ibikoresho bya COVID-19.
Abakozi bo muri iri tsinda ry'ibyago ntibakunze gukenera imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda bishobora gukoreshwa mu kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bari mu ndege, harimo gutandukanya umurwayi n'abandi bantu, no gushyira intera nibura y'ibirenge 6, gushyiraho abakozi bo kwita ku muntu urwaye no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa, no kumusaba ko yambara umwenda w'umunwa n'uw'impumuro mu gihe asusurutsa cyangwa yitsamura.
Abakozi bo mu modoka bagomba kwambara intoki z'ubuvuzi zikoreshwa rimwe mu gihe bakorera umuntu urwaye cyangwa bakagira aho bahurira n'imyanda cyangwa ahantu hashobora kwandurira, kandi niba umurwayi arwaye afite umuriro, guhekenya kenshi cyangwa guhumeka nabi, niba bishoboka, bakoresha ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu mifuka y'ibikoresho by'ibitaro, aho ubutaka bwanduye bugomba guhanagurwa no gukorerwa umuti wo guhanagura indwara nyuma yo gukora. Ku byoherezwa mu bucuruzi, harimo no gutwara abantu mu bwato bw'ubwato bw'ubwato cyangwa ubundi bwato bw'abashyitsi, kugenzura ibyago birimo guhagarika ingendo mu gihe umuntu arwaye, kwigunga no kumenyesha abaganga b'ubwato ako kanya mu gihe umuntu abonye umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana imiti bigomba gukorwa mu cyumba cy'umuntu wihariye. CDC irasaba ko amashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana bifungwa by'agateganyo mu gihe gito, hatitawe ku mibare y'icyorezo mu baturage, kugira ngo bakore isuku no guhanagura indwara, kubera ko umuntu ufite ubwandu ashobora kuba yaragiye mu kigo cy'ishuri.
Iyo ubwandu bukomeje kuba buke cyangwa buciriritse, hari uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu, nko guhagarika inkambi, amateraniro n'ibindi bikorwa nk'amasomo y'abantu cyangwa kuririmba cyangwa gusangira mu kafeteri, kongera umwanya w'ameza, guhindura amasaha yo gutangira no gusoza, kugabanya abakiriya batagikenewe no gukoresha ibiro by'ubuzima byitandukanyije ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Iyo mu karere habaye ubwandu bukomeye, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda, birakenewe ko amashuri afungurwa igihe kirekire. CDC yemera ko hari ibyago bike by'ubuzima ku bakozi b'amategeko bakora imirimo yabo ya buri munsi.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba kuvugana n'abantu barwaye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 bagirwa inama yo gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi bw'ibanze, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Iyo habayeho gutinya kwandura mu gihe cy'ubwirinzi, abakozi bagomba gukaraba no guhanagura imyenda yabo n'ibikoresho byabo by'akazi mbere yo kongera kubikoresha bakoresheje imiti cyangwa udusenda, kandi bakagendera ku mabwiriza y'akazi ajyanye no kubika no kujugunya ibikoresho bya bwite bikoreshwa, no kubika no kumesa imyenda yanduye.
OSHA yemera ko bamwe mu bakozi mu nzego z'ubuzima n'iz'ubuvuzi bashyizwe mu byiciro by'imirimo iteje akaga cyangwa iteje akaga cyane.
Imirimo y'ibyago, urugero nk'abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima, abashinzwe gushyigikira, abakora mu mavuriro n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi, bashobora guhura n'abarwayi banduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Iyo abakozi bakoresha uburyo bwo gutangiza aerosol, cyangwa bakagenda bafata ibipimo by'abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19, baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwanduza.
Mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi by'umuriro harimo guterwa imiyoboro, kugabanya ububabare bw'umuriro, gupima mu bwonko, gukora ibizamini bimwe na bimwe by'amenyo n'ubuvuzi, cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'ibicurane.
Akazi ko mu cyumba cy'ubuvuzi giteye ubwoba ni akazi ko gutegura imirambo y'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19 nyuma yo gupfa; iyo umuntu apfuye, ibyo bikorwa biba ari akazi gafite ibyago byinshi. Ibindi byangombwa by'ubwubatsi bigomba kwitabwaho kuri aya matsinda y'ibyago, harimo ibyumba byo gutandukanya abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19, cyane cyane mu gihe habaho uburyo bwo gukora inganda z'ubumara.
Mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'isuku, guhumeka mu cyumba bishobora kuba byiza.
Ibipimo bigomba gutwarwa hakurikijwe ingamba zo kwirinda za Biodefense Level 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi bashya bashyirwa mu byumba by'abarwayi bibarirwa mu bihumbi, bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. OSHA yasabye ko abakora ahantu hatandukanye n'abarwayi cyangwa abantu bakekwaho SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa abakora imikorere yo kuvura imyanda, bakoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe cy'ubundi buryo bwo kwirinda.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, mu rwego rw'umushinga w'ubwirinzi bw'ubuhumekero wemewe kandi urimo ibipimo by'amaso, imyitozo n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi, bikenewe gukoresha udupfukamunwa N95 twemewe na NIOSH cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byiza.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi bugatuma abakozi barushaho kumererwa neza. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ntirikangurira abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa twongera ubukana, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero kandi idashobora gukwirakwizwa ahanini binyuze mu byuka byo mu mubiri.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko abakozi batangira gukora ibizamini bakoresha udupfukamunwa gusa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye abantu bakenera, bagakoresha cyangwa bakazana ibipimo by'ubuhumekero by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 batakoze ubuvuzi bwa Aerosol, kwambara udupfukamunwa, udushumi, udupfukamunwa n'utugombambaro.
Iyo hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo guhanagura umwuka, agapfukamunwa kabaga gakoreshwa mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi gasimbuzwa agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko gutanga PPE ku isi hose bidakenewe, OMS isaba ko hakorwa ingamba zikurikira kugira ngo hakoreshwe ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe: Telemedicine (ubuvuzi bwa kure), gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nka za clinique, kureka abarwayi ba COVID-19 kwinjira mu cyumba gusa ku bantu bafasha mu buryo butaziguye, gukoresha PPE gusa mu bikorwa by'ingenzi, gukoresha agapfukamunwa mu gihe bitabwaho n'abarwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza urubuga rwa PPE, no gushishikariza abantu badafite ibimenyetso gukoresha agapfukamunwa mu buryo busanzwe.
