Angiotensin 2B (ACE2) ni enzymes ifata ku bice by'inyuma (uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo) by'amaraso, amaraso, umutima, ipfunwe n'umura.
ACE2 irwanya ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin binyuze mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin 2 no kongera ingano ya angiotensin (1-7), bigatuma iba umuti ufasha cyane mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'aho yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo zimwe na zimwe za virusi zigendana na virusi.
Ubwoko bwa enzymes mu bantu bwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 ihindura enzyme irimo metaloenzime ifite ingirabuzimafatizo, iri ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu maraso no mu yandi.
Poroteyine ACE2 ikubiyemo intera ya M2 ya peptidease na intera ya C-terminal ya amino acid cysterin.
ACE2 ni poroteyine y'umura ifite uruhu rumwe rukora mu buryo bwa enzymatic, ikora ku mubiri w'uruhu no mu bindi binyabuzima.
Uruhu rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 rwatandukanywa n'urundi rugingo rw'umushongi witwa shdaze, maze poroteyine y'umuti iboneka mu maraso, amaherezo ikavanwa mu cyondo.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata mu gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha, intaro nto, intanga z'amaraso, intanga z'amaraso n'intanga z'imitsi y'amaraso mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
ACE2 mRNA iboneka kandi mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu mubiri w'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubuhumekero n'igiti cy'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'umuhuza wa ACE.
ACE isenya ingirabuzimafatizo yitwa angiotensin 1 ikavamo angiotensin 2 ikora nk'umuti uhagarika imitsi.
ACE2 ihindura, ifata amino acid ya phenylalanine carboxyl-terminal ikavanamo angiotensin 2 (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikajya mu cyiciro cya angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
