Byagaragaye ko ACE2 y'umuntu (rhACE2), uburyo bushya bwo kuvura indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha, bwafashije mu kuzamura imikorere y'ibihaha n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube zifite indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka mu buryo butarangwa n'ubushake bw'ibinyamubiri.
Igihe cy'igice cya kabiri cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha 10, kandi kigira iminota 30 yo gutangira gukora, n'amasaha 24 yo gukora.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi butandukanye byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizeye ku bantu batagira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya inzitiramibu zisanzwe za sisitemu ya renine-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa mu barwayi bafite igihe kirekire cy'ingingo ya angiotensin II.
"Ibipimo bya COVID-19 B ni porogaramu za software za terefone zigendanwa zigamije gufasha gukurikirana guhamagara mu gisubizo cy'icyorezo cya 2019-20 coronavirus, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu ufite ubwandu".
Porogaramu nyinshi zatanzwe cyangwa zitezwe mu turere tumwe na tumwe hamwe n'intara zashyigikiwe na leta.
Hakozwe imikorere itandukanye yo gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana itumanaho.
Hari impungenge ku bijyanye n'ibanga, cyane cyane ku bijyanye na sisitemu zikora ku buryo bwo gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu za telefoni ngendanwa bari.
Amahitamo adashishikaje cyane harimo gukoresha Bluetooth kugirango hamenyekane aho umuntu ari hafi ya telefoni zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko byongeye gushyiramo ubushobozi bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth ku buryo butaziguye kuri Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu yemerera abaturage kureba niba bagiranye imishyikirano n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Iri gukoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapuru, porogaramu yitwa Tris Tugdre irakoreshwa.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'ikoranabuhanga mu by'amakuru, yashyizwe ahagaragara nk'umwandiko ukingutse, kandi igomba gushyikirizwa leta. Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ya telefone igendanwa yitwa "StopKorona!", ikoresha Bluetooth mu gukurikirana abantu bashobora kwandura, ituma abayobozi b'ubuzima bagira icyo bakora vuba.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Guhera ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play na Apple App Store.
"Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere kandi ko izaba igomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyi iteganyijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid"")".
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande zirimo gutekereza ku porogaramu ishingiye kuri porogaramu ya Tris Togder ya Singapore na protokol ya Bluetris. Uburusiya bufite gahunda yo gukora porogaramu ya geo-fence ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 kandi batuye i Moscou kugirango birinde gusohoka mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano, yashyize ku rutonde ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere y'ibikoresho, harimo ibinyoma byemeza ko byakozwe n'abantu bake cyane, n'uko byatinda gukora neza mu gihe porogaramu ikoreshwa ku bantu bake cyane.
"Mu guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry' porogaramu ziyobya cyangwa zangiza za ""coronavirus"", Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bigo bishobora kongeramo porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus mububiko bwa App Store, ibigabanya gusa ku bigo ""byemewe"" cyangwa byemewe".
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye uburenganzira bw'abantu bagaragaje impungenge ku ikoreshwa ry'ubwiteganyirize bw'abantu benshi hakoreshejwe porogaramu za coronavirus, cyane cyane ku bijyanye no gusenya ibikorwa remezo by'ubwiteganyirize byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus nyuma y'uko icyorezo cya virusi cyakemutse.
