Gukurikirana guhamagarwa kw'ibanga ni igitekerezo cyemewe cyakoze ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuva nibura mu 2013. Guhera ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'inzobere arimo gukora ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth ifite ingufu nke (BLE) kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona aho ari hafi ya telefoni zigendanwa.
Ariko kandi, PEPP-PT ni gahunda yo guhuza, ikubiyemo uburyo bwihariye kandi budafite aho bugarukira, kandi ntabwo ari porogaramu imwe. Porogaramu zidakomeye zirimo gukurikirana hamwe no kubungabunga ubuzima bwite (DP-PPT / DP-3T), umubare w'amatelefone ya TCN, umubare w'amatelefone ya FKA, CEN), porogaramu ziteje imbere ubuzima bwite, na sisitemu yo gukurikirana amatelefone ngendanwa (PACT), n'ibindi.
Muri izo poroteyine, amakuru agaragaza umuntu ku giti cye ntajya asiga imodoka, kandi amakuru yose agakurikiranwa mu modoka.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ririmo gukora SafePaths, urubuga rukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gihe cyo gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari cyangwa aho ahurira n'umuhanda kugira ngo agere ku cyorezo cya COVID-19.
