Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga rya TCN ryashinzwe n'amatsinda yibanze ku buryo bumwe n'amabwiriza y'ubufatanye, agamije kugabanya ubwiganze no gutuma habaho ubufatanye ku isi hose mu gukurikirana no gutanga imiburo - ikintu cy'ingenzi mu kugera ku bwubahane bukomeye.
