Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura sisitemu z'ikoranabuhanga za Android na iOS, byatangaje udushya mu gukurikirana abakoresha, bishingiye ku ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth ry'ingufu nke n'ibanga ryo kubara amakuru, bavuga ko ari bwo bufasha abantu kubungabunga ubuzima bwite.
Nanone batangaje ibijyanye na tekiniki z'ibanze zikoreshwa muri iyo gahunda.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi sisitemu iteganijwe mu byiciro bitatu:
Gutangaza ibikoresho bishya byo guha ubutegetsi ubushobozi bwo gushyiraho gahunda zo gukurikirana virusi ya corona mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, ariko bigakomeza kubahiriza ubuzima bwite.
Guhuza byimazeyo iyi mikorere muri iOS na Android; Google na Apple bigamije gukemura ibibazo byo kugabanya kugura no kugenzura igihe cyose, bigamije kubanza gukwirakwiza sisitemu binyuze mu buryo bwo gutangaza sisitemu, hanyuma nyuma yo guhangana n'akaga, bakaza kuyikuraho mu buryo bumwe.
Gukoresha imiti b (bimwe mubyitwa guhindura imiti, guhindura imiterere, kongera gukoresha cyangwa guhindura umuti) ni ugukoresha imiti yemewe mu kuvura indwara cyangwa ikibazo gitandukanye n'icyo umuti watangiwe.
Ni igice cy'ubushakashatsi muri iki gihe, bugamije gukora imiti yo kuvura COVID-19 ifite umutekano kandi ikora.
Ibindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi birimo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa plasma mu bantu bakize. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine 66 zishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara, buri poroteyine ikaba ifite ahantu hatandukanye ho gufungira.
